   STEP_SEQ DB 01H, 02H, 04H, 08H, 10H, 20H
   MODE DB 2 DUP(00H)
   
   
   
   
DATA ENDS

CODE SEGMENT
   ASSUME CS:CODE, DS:DATA
      ORG 0000H
      
